 pro pic to leave this comment??"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T07:50:48.000Z","msg":"Yes but no"},{"pid":"118fec00a4871954aef22ae57f151090aa1424f5","tid":2506143,"uid":41818,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"2dfb9768bd7c53ff160e5e6121daa92230bcf912","tid":2506143,"uid":42190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T07:21:57.000Z","msg":"做乜佢2個咁多野嘈"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T12:46:43.000Z","msg":"2004年一餐晚飯交惡<br />\n<br />\n兩人都對太空生活很有堅持，但超過16年恩怨，卻是因為2004年的一餐晚飯。兩人遇上了還熱烈辯論「人類點上太空」的話題，兩人就火箭設計不咬弦，Bezos無視大部分Musk的意見，自此兩人就陷入「冷戰」；直到2013年，兩人在爭奪NASA的發射台一事上全面交惡，SpaceX 正努力爭取獨家使用權，Bezos卻以Blue Origin高調入紙反對；當年Musk就此事大發雷霆，認為Bezos過去10年研發不多，入紙只是扮晒反對。最終Bezos反對無效，SpaceX 贏得使用權，成為第一家向國際空間站運送物資的商業公司。<br />\n<br />\n豈料2014年，兩人更陷入了patent之戰，原來，Bezos搶先注冊了無人機太空船的patent，SpaceX 認為所謂專利，已經有咗幾個世紀，不明白為何可以有專利，Musk決定訴諸法庭，最後Blue Origin敗訴，專利被取消，Musk又勝一仗。"},{"pid":"cf05545d6db87c55af292954075bc71f52e4e956","tid":2506143,"uid":41818,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f96b318b7282182f59e86c4717c4f5902fa47814","tid":2506143,"uid":52675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T07:42:21.000Z","msg":"NASA原先預期將從這3間公司選擇2間，再進行最後競逐，但未料NASA最後一刻突然改變規則<br />\n<br />\n咁撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嬲都合理既"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T12:50:31.000Z","msg":"應該發現光頭佬唔會整得出d咩出嚟 直接放棄唔等"},{"pid":"e48ed199c111ca84e36f5cd2328b8b1d41bd3834","tid":2506143,"uid":40267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"118fec00a4871954aef22ae57f151090aa1424f5","tid":2506143,"uid":41818,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"2dfb9768bd7c53ff160e5e6121daa92230bcf912","tid":2506143,"uid":42190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T07:21:57.000Z","msg":"做乜佢2個咁多野嘈"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T12:46:43.000Z","msg":"2004年一餐晚飯交惡<br />\n<br />\n兩人都對太空生活很有堅持，但超過16年恩怨，卻是因為2004年的一餐晚飯。兩人遇上了還熱烈辯論「人類點上太空」的話題，兩人就火箭設計不咬弦，Bezos無視大部分Musk的意見，自此兩人就陷入「冷戰」；直到2013年，兩人在爭奪NASA的發射台一事上全面交惡，SpaceX 正努力爭取獨家使用權，Bezos卻以Blue Origin高調入紙反對；當年Musk就此事大發雷霆，認為Bezos過去10年研發不多，入紙只是扮晒反對。最終Bezos反對無效，SpaceX 贏得使用權，成為第一家向國際空間站運送物資的商業公司。<br />\n<br />\n豈料2014年，兩人更陷入了patent之戰，原來，Bezos搶先注冊了無人機太空船的patent，SpaceX 認為所謂專利，已經有咗幾個世紀，不明白為何可以有專利，Musk決定訴諸法庭，最後Blue Origin敗訴，專利被取消，Musk又勝一仗。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T04:43:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"397aa22250cad92e50db47f159d06d0c19cbd49f","tid":2506143,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T04:50:29.000Z","msg":"抵撚死光頭佬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ad972f6619e10e6a0ca79445ede48548d064507","tid":2506143,"uid":69231,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T04:51:38.000Z","msg":"Jeff who?#haha#do"},{"pid":"fc2e1e7f0da0d87c9864a086cf88af7270955437","tid":2506143,"uid":81925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e48ed199c111ca84e36f5cd2328b8b1d41bd3834","tid":2506143,"uid":40267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"118fec00a4871954aef22ae57f151090aa1424f5","tid":2506143,"uid":41818,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"2dfb9768bd7c53ff160e5e6121daa92230bcf912","tid":2506143,"uid":42190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T07:21:57.000Z","msg":"做乜佢2個咁多野嘈"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T12:46:43.000Z","msg":"2004年一餐晚飯交惡<br />\n<br />\n兩人都對太空生活很有堅持，但超過16年恩怨，卻是因為2004年的一餐晚飯。兩人遇上了還熱烈辯論「人類點上太空」的話題，兩人就火箭設計不咬弦，Bezos無視大部分Musk的意見，自此兩人就陷入「冷戰」；直到2013年，兩人在爭奪NASA的發射台一事上全面交惡，SpaceX 正努力爭取獨家使用權，Bezos卻以Blue Origin高調入紙反對；當年Musk就此事大發雷霆，認為Bezos過去10年研發不多，入紙只是扮晒反對。最終Bezos反對無效，SpaceX 贏得使用權，成為第一家向國際空間站運送物資的商業公司。<br />\n<br />\n豈料2014年，兩人更陷入了patent之戰，原來，Bezos搶先注冊了無人機太空船的patent，SpaceX 認為所謂專利，已經有咗幾個世紀，不明白為何可以有專利，Musk決定訴諸法庭，最後Blue Origin敗訴，專利被取消，Musk又勝一仗。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T04:43:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T04:52:01.000Z","msg":"光頭佬呢D生意佬唔好阻住個地頭轉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caeb806a3ca7db1677c90ccf2693bd33ee952a6a","tid":2506143,"uid":207247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08df2c3794f6a59ad1c8bf531befb34af99d9d60","tid":2506143,"uid":49316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T07:45:37.000Z","msg":"光頭佬大把錢打官司<br />\n<br />\n國防部個JEDI contract輸俾M$係咁告政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T04:53:37.000Z","msg":"2邊都大把錢，打咪打囉（官司）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be0f55dd2a1cffd13b3ad39992c79bfa07937ab6","tid":2506143,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T04:54:34.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n貴婦狗版"},{"pid":"162f0387d22c6d755b4948bf510e811b517e7846","tid":2506143,"uid":33618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T04:55:58.000Z","msg":"Cloud又輸，Space又輸，光頭佬搞咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBTW, 捨得拆股未？"},{"pid":"af4f97ff4f284a43801d5f6f76523df7a93f7cbb","tid":2506143,"uid":212727,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T04:57:16.000Z","msg":"其實佢咁講係仲要笑埋Jeff支火箭個樣似一碌..........................<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmP3pHEuHtz5KQtxF5be2jb9icigScub4J3612wefYrUFL?filename=p60yX8H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp60yX8